  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Classic educational life simulator in modern twist!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Be the first to achieve all four main goals: wealth, happiness, work experience, and education.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2855500/extras/7aa38ffeb2fcfb183df97d2e4da4b6e5.poster.avif?t=1766169196\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2855500/extras/7aa38ffeb2fcfb183df97d2e4da4b6e5.webm?t=1766169196\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2855500/extras/7aa38ffeb2fcfb183df97d2e4da4b6e5.mp4?t=1766169196\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play solo against computer, team up with friends in multiplayer (up to 4 players), or take turns in hot seat mode (up to 4 players+computer).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Balance your needs by eating, finding a job, spending free time, pursuing education to unlock better careers, and shopping for various consumer goods. Watch out for random events like market crash, fire, road blockade and more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a vibrant map filled with essential locations: job office, bank, mall, university, market, pawn shop and more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2855500/extras/ff375eeab42e92cf9688e1c347a37473.poster.avif?t=1766169196\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2855500/extras/ff375eeab42e92cf9688e1c347a37473.webm?t=1766169196\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2855500/extras/ff375eeab42e92cf9688e1c347a37473.mp4?t=1766169196\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect 50 unique hats to personalize your avatar and unlock achievements.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2855500/extras/e5a2b37272ea59f1b54956a4b2d267cc.poster.avif?t=1766169196\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2855500/extras/e5a2b37272ea59f1b54956a4b2d267cc.webm?t=1766169196\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2855500/extras/e5a2b37272ea59f1b54956a4b2d267cc.mp4?t=1766169196\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 200 items to buy, including your home furnishing</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2855500/extras/327c06d12557e875cd3f0fa6cad75cae.poster.avif?t=1766169196\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2855500/extras/327c06d12557e875cd3f0fa6cad75cae.webm?t=1766169196\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2855500/extras/327c06d12557e875cd3f0fa6cad75cae.mp4?t=1766169196\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 150 weekend cards to choose from and more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2855500/extras/d09161f3b3cd92060b8b3da45781235d.poster.avif?t=1766169196\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2855500/extras/d09161f3b3cd92060b8b3da45781235d.webm?t=1766169196\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2855500/extras/d09161f3b3cd92060b8b3da45781235d.mp4?t=1766169196\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Classic educational life simulator in modern twist!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Be the first to achieve all four main goals: wealth, happiness, work experience, and education.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2855500/extras/7aa38ffeb2fcfb183df97d2e4da4b6e5.poster.avif?t=1766169196\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2855500/extras/7aa38ffeb2fcfb183df97d2e4da4b6e5.webm?t=1766169196\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2855500/extras/7aa38ffeb2fcfb183df97d2e4da4b6e5.mp4?t=1766169196\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play solo against computer, team up with friends in multiplayer (up to 4 players), or take turns in hot seat mode (up to 4 players+computer).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Balance your needs by eating, finding a job, spending free time, pursuing education to unlock better careers, and shopping for various consumer goods. Watch out for random events like market crash, fire, road blockade and more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a vibrant map filled with essential locations: job office, bank, mall, university, market, pawn shop and more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2855500/extras/ff375eeab42e92cf9688e1c347a37473.poster.avif?t=1766169196\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2855500/extras/ff375eeab42e92cf9688e1c347a37473.webm?t=1766169196\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\